des: This flash news briefing provides a short summary of news and events relevant to the California workers' compensation claims industry. The feed is maintained by lawyers from the Floyd Skeren Manukian Langevin, L.L.P. defense firm, and instructors from the WorkCompAcademy.com online school. Topic include case law, regulatory events, fraud prosecutions, and medical news.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
